data.description: Welcome to 640 N Crenshaw Ct.  located in  the area of Robinwood Estates in Visalia,CA. This home is located in a cul-de-sac and offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, 2 car garage and a good size backyard that can be made into your own. With roof only being about 7 years old and HVAC system  recently replaced, you might just need to bring your painter and  update a few cosmetic items before you make this home your own.
